This paper focuses on the analysis of API forums, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves finding relevant information from a large dataset. The paper also mentions the use of automated solutions, which could fall under natural language processing (cs.CL) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) as it involves protecting sensitive information. Finally, the study of developer forums could also fall under social and information networks (cs.SI) as it involves analyzing interactions between users.
